        <h2>
            神学政治论的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 13 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5400370">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5400370/" class="title-link">斯宾诺莎 《神学政治论（Tractatus Theologico -...</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5400370"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/jiangxulin/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u47643947-54.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/jiangxulin/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">江绪林</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-04-23"
      class="main-meta">2012-04-23 00:11:48</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5400370_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                       【按语：斯宾诺莎的《神学政治论》是一部颇让我困惑的作品。如同书名Tractatus Theologico-Politicus可以翻译为“神学的-政治的专门论文”，中间那个破折号似乎指示了该书本身的一个断裂。斯宾诺莎宣称他的主要目的是“把信仰与哲学分开”。这一方面通过严谨的《圣经》文...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5400370/#comments">(6回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">15有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
